<section class="space-y-6">
  <div
    class="space-y-2 text-center"
    data-aos="fade-up"
    data-aos-duration="600"
    data-aos-easing="ease-out"
  >
    <p
      class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-base-content/70"
    >
      Before & After
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">
      Reshaping a tired pool area into a crisp retreat
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-base-content/80">
      We drained an aging pool, replaced chipped tiles, repainted the shell
      walls, and finished the surrounds so the entire terrace matches the rest
      of the home.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
    <article
      class="card border border-base-300 bg-base-100 shadow-sm"
      data-aos="zoom-in"
      data-aos-duration="450"
      data-aos-easing="ease-out"
    >
      <div class="card-body space-y-3">
        <p
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-base-content/70"
        >
          Before
        </p>
        <picture class="block overflow-hidden rounded-2xl">
          <source srcset="/images/before.webp" type="image/webp" />
          <img
            src="/images/before.jpg"
            alt="Drained concrete pool with chipped tiles, exposed shell, and scattered debris"
            class="h-64 w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </picture>
        <p class="text-base-content/80">
          Weathered coping, stained plaster, and debris made the pool feel
          unfinished and disconnected from the garden.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article
      class="card border border-base-300 bg-primary text-primary-content shadow-sm"
      data-aos="zoom-in"
      data-aos-duration="450"
      data-aos-delay="150"
      data-aos-easing="ease-out"
    >
      <div class="card-body space-y-3">
        <p
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-primary-content/80"
        >
          After
        </p>
        <picture class="block overflow-hidden rounded-2xl">
          <source srcset="/images/after.webp" type="image/webp" />
          <img
            src="/images/after.jpg"
            alt="Renovated pool with crisp white render, fresh tiles, and tidy planting around the coping"
            class="h-64 w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </picture>
        <p class="text-primary-content/90">
          Clean render, new tiles, and simple poolside detailing give the
          terrace a calm, finished feel.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
